    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-6727_10344_000034_000002",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/6727/10344/6727_10344_000034_000002.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-6727",
        "content": "Light therefore is not a sensible quality.",
        "style_prompt": "M_p-low_s-normal_e-normal",
        "gender": "M",
        "pitch": "low",
        "speed": "normal",
        "energy": "normal"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-6727_10344_000035_000001",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/6727/10344/6727_10344_000035_000001.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-6727",
        "content": "But the light of the heavenly bodies is a cause of substantial forms of earthly bodies, and also gives to colors their immaterial being, by making them actually visible.",
        "style_prompt": "M_p-low_s-slow_e-normal",
        "gender": "M",
        "pitch": "low",
        "speed": "slow",
        "energy": "normal"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-6727_10344_000035_000002",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/6727/10344/6727_10344_000035_000002.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-6727",
        "content": "Light, then, is not a sensible quality, but rather a substantial or spiritual form.",
        "style_prompt": "M_p-low_s-slow_e-low",
        "gender": "M",
        "pitch": "low",
        "speed": "slow",
        "energy": "low"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-6727_10344_000037_000001",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/6727/10344/6727_10344_000037_000001.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-6727",
        "content": "But this cannot be the case for two reasons.",
        "style_prompt": "M_p-normal_s-normal_e-low",
        "gender": "M",
        "pitch": "normal",
        "speed": "normal",
        "energy": "low"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-6727_10344_000037_000002",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/6727/10344/6727_10344_000037_000002.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-6727",
        "content": "First, because light gives a name to the air, since by it the air becomes actually luminous.",
        "style_prompt": "M_p-normal_s-slow_e-normal",
        "gender": "M",
        "pitch": "normal",
        "speed": "slow",
        "energy": "normal"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-6727_10344_000037_000003",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/6727/10344/6727_10344_000037_000003.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-6727",
        "content": "But color does not do this, for we do not speak of the air as colored.",
        "style_prompt": "M_p-high_s-slow_e-low",
        "gender": "M",
        "pitch": "high",
        "speed": "slow",
        "energy": "very low"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-6727_10344_000037_000004",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/6727/10344/6727_10344_000037_000004.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-6727",
        "content": "Secondly, because light produces natural effects, for by the rays of the sun bodies are warmed, and natural changes cannot be brought about by mere intentions.",
        "style_prompt": "M_p-low_s-normal_e-low",
        "gender": "M",
        "pitch": "low",
        "speed": "normal",
        "energy": "very low"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-6727_10344_000037_000005",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/6727/10344/6727_10344_000037_000005.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-6727",
        "content": "Others have said that light is the sun's substantial form, but this also seems impossible for two reasons.",
        "style_prompt": "M_p-low_s-slow_e-normal",
        "gender": "M",
        "pitch": "low",
        "speed": "slow",
        "energy": "normal"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-6727_10344_000037_000007",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/6727/10344/6727_10344_000037_000007.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-6727",
        "content": "In the second place, because it is impossible that what is the substantial form of one thing should be the accidental form of another; since substantial forms of their very nature constitute species: wherefore the substantial form always and everywhere accompanies the species.",
        "style_prompt": "M_p-low_s-normal_e-normal",
        "gender": "M",
        "pitch": "low",
        "speed": "normal",
        "energy": "normal"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-6727_10344_000037_000008",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/6727/10344/6727_10344_000037_000008.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-6727",
        "content": "But light is not the substantial form of air, for if it were, the air would be destroyed when light is withdrawn.",
        "style_prompt": "M_p-normal_s-normal_e-normal",
        "gender": "M",
        "pitch": "normal",
        "speed": "normal",
        "energy": "normal"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-6727_10344_000037_000009",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/6727/10344/6727_10344_000037_000009.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-6727",
        "content": "Hence it cannot be the substantial form of the sun",
        "style_prompt": "M_p-normal_s-normal_e-normal",
        "gender": "M",
        "pitch": "normal",
        "speed": "normal",
        "energy": "normal"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-6727_10344_000038_000001",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/6727/10344/6727_10344_000038_000001.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-6727",
        "content": "A proof of this is that the rays of different stars produce different effects according to the diverse natures of bodies.",
        "style_prompt": "M_p-normal_s-slow_e-normal",
        "gender": "M",
        "pitch": "normal",
        "speed": "slow",
        "energy": "normal"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-6727_10344_000039_000001",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/6727/10344/6727_10344_000039_000001.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-6727",
        "content": "For when matter receives its form perfectly, the qualities consequent upon the form are firm and enduring; as when, for instance, water is converted into fire.",
        "style_prompt": "M_p-low_s-slow_e-low",
        "gender": "M",
        "pitch": "low",
        "speed": "slow",
        "energy": "very low"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-6727_10344_000039_000002",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/6727/10344/6727_10344_000039_000002.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-6727",
        "content": "When, however, substantial form is received imperfectly, so as to be, as it were, in process of being received, rather than fully impressed, the consequent quality lasts for a time but is not permanent; as may be seen when water which has been heated returns in time to its natural state.",
        "style_prompt": "M_p-low_s-slow_e-low",
        "gender": "M",
        "pitch": "low",
        "speed": "slow",
        "energy": "very low"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-6727_10344_000039_000003",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/6727/10344/6727_10344_000039_000003.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-6727",
        "content": "But light is not produced by the transmutation of matter, as though matter were in receipt of a substantial form, and light were a certain inception of substantial form.",
        "style_prompt": "M_p-low_s-normal_e-normal",
        "gender": "M",
        "pitch": "low",
        "speed": "normal",
        "energy": "normal"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-6727_10344_000039_000004",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/6727/10344/6727_10344_000039_000004.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-6727",
        "content": "For this reason light disappears on the disappearance of its active cause.",
        "style_prompt": "M_p-low_s-slow_e-low",
        "gender": "M",
        "pitch": "low",
        "speed": "slow",
        "energy": "low"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-6727_10344_000043_000000",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/6727/10344/6727_10344_000043_000000.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-6727",
        "content": "Whether the Production of Light Is Fittingly Assigned to the First Day?",
        "style_prompt": "M_p-low_s-normal_e-normal",
        "gender": "M",
        "pitch": "low",
        "speed": "normal",
        "energy": "normal"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-6727_10344_000044_000000",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/6727/10344/6727_10344_000044_000000.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-6727",
        "content": "Objection one: It would seem that the production of light is not fittingly assigned to the first day.",
        "style_prompt": "M_p-normal_s-slow_e-low",
        "gender": "M",
        "pitch": "normal",
        "speed": "slow",
        "energy": "low"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-6727_10344_000044_000002",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/6727/10344/6727_10344_000044_000002.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-6727",
        "content": "But qualities are accidents, and as such should have, not the first, but a subordinate place.",
        "style_prompt": "M_p-normal_s-slow_e-low",
        "gender": "M",
        "pitch": "normal",
        "speed": "slow",
        "energy": "low"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-6727_10344_000044_000003",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/6727/10344/6727_10344_000044_000003.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-6727",
        "content": "The production of light, then, ought not to be assigned to the first day.",
        "style_prompt": "M_p-low_s-normal_e-low",
        "gender": "M",
        "pitch": "very low",
        "speed": "normal",
        "energy": "very low"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-6727_10344_000045_000001",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/6727/10344/6727_10344_000045_000001.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-6727",
        "content": "Therefore the production of light could not have been on the first day.",
        "style_prompt": "M_p-normal_s-normal_e-high",
        "gender": "M",
        "pitch": "normal",
        "speed": "normal",
        "energy": "high"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-6727_10344_000046_000001",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/6727/10344/6727_10344_000046_000001.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-6727",
        "content": "But movement of this kind is an attribute of the firmament, and we read that the firmament was made on the second day.",
        "style_prompt": "M_p-high_s-normal_e-normal",
        "gender": "M",
        "pitch": "high",
        "speed": "normal",
        "energy": "normal"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-6727_10344_000046_000002",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/6727/10344/6727_10344_000046_000002.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-6727",
        "content": "Therefore the production of light, dividing night from day, ought not to be assigned to the first day.",
        "style_prompt": "M_p-normal_s-normal_e-normal",
        "gender": "M",
        "pitch": "normal",
        "speed": "normal",
        "energy": "normal"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-6727_10344_000047_000002",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/6727/10344/6727_10344_000047_000002.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-6727",
        "content": "Therefore the production of light ought not to be assigned to the first day.",
        "style_prompt": "M_p-normal_s-normal_e-normal",
        "gender": "M",
        "pitch": "normal",
        "speed": "normal",
        "energy": "normal"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-6727_10344_000048_000001",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/6727/10344/6727_10344_000048_000001.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-6727",
        "content": "But there can be no day without light.",
        "style_prompt": "M_p-normal_s-slow_e-high",
        "gender": "M",
        "pitch": "normal",
        "speed": "slow",
        "energy": "high"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-6727_10344_000048_000002",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/6727/10344/6727_10344_000048_000002.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-6727",
        "content": "Therefore light must have been made on the first day.",
        "style_prompt": "M_p-low_s-slow_e-normal",
        "gender": "M",
        "pitch": "low",
        "speed": "slow",
        "energy": "normal"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-6727_10344_000049_000002",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/6727/10344/6727_10344_000049_000002.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-6727",
        "content": "The forming, therefore, of this spiritual nature is signified by the production of light, that is to say, of spiritual light.",
        "style_prompt": "M_p-high_s-normal_e-high",
        "gender": "M",
        "pitch": "high",
        "speed": "normal",
        "energy": "high"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-6727_10344_000049_000003",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/6727/10344/6727_10344_000049_000003.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-6727",
        "content": "For a spiritual nature receives its form by the enlightenment whereby it is led to adhere to the Word of God.",
        "style_prompt": "M_p-normal_s-normal_e-high",
        "gender": "M",
        "pitch": "normal",
        "speed": "normal",
        "energy": "high"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-6727_10344_000050_000000",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/6727/10344/6727_10344_000050_000000.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-6727",
        "content": "Other writers think that the production of spiritual creatures was purposely omitted by Moses, and give various reasons.",
        "style_prompt": "M_p-normal_s-slow_e-low",
        "gender": "M",
        "pitch": "normal",
        "speed": "slow",
        "energy": "low"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-6727_10344_000052_000000",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/6727/10344/6727_10344_000052_000000.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-6727",
        "content": "But mention is made of several kinds of formlessness, in regard to the corporeal creature.",
        "style_prompt": "M_p-low_s-slow_e-normal",
        "gender": "M",
        "pitch": "low",
        "speed": "slow",
        "energy": "normal"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-6727_10344_000052_000003",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/6727/10344/6727_10344_000052_000003.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-6727",
        "content": "The second reason is because light is a common quality.",
        "style_prompt": "M_p-high_s-normal_e-high",
        "gender": "M",
        "pitch": "high",
        "speed": "normal",
        "energy": "high"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-6727_10344_000052_000004",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/6727/10344/6727_10344_000052_000004.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-6727",
        "content": "For light is common to terrestrial and celestial bodies.",
        "style_prompt": "M_p-normal_s-slow_e-high",
        "gender": "M",
        "pitch": "normal",
        "speed": "slow",
        "energy": "high"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-6727_10344_000052_000008",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/6727/10344/6727_10344_000052_000008.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-6727",
        "content": "It was fitting, then, as an evidence of the Divine wisdom, that among the works of distinction the production of light should take first place, since light is a form of the primary body, and because it is more common quality.",
        "style_prompt": "M_p-normal_s-normal_e-normal",
        "gender": "M",
        "pitch": "normal",
        "speed": "normal",
        "energy": "normal"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-6727_10344_000053_000001",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/6727/10344/6727_10344_000053_000001.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-6727",
        "content": "And there is yet a fourth, already touched upon in the objections; that day cannot be unless light exists, which was made therefore on the first day.",
        "style_prompt": "M_p-low_s-slow_e-low",
        "gender": "M",
        "pitch": "very low",
        "speed": "slow",
        "energy": "very low"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-6727_10344_000055_000001",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/6727/10344/6727_10344_000055_000001.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-6727",
        "content": "But this cannot well be maintained, as in the beginning of genesis Holy Scripture records the institution of that order of nature which henceforth is to endure.",
        "style_prompt": "M_p-normal_s-normal_e-normal",
        "gender": "M",
        "pitch": "normal",
        "speed": "normal",
        "energy": "normal"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-6727_10344_000055_000002",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/6727/10344/6727_10344_000055_000002.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-6727",
        "content": "We cannot, then, say that what was made at that time afterwards ceased to exist.",
        "style_prompt": "M_p-low_s-slow_e-normal",
        "gender": "M",
        "pitch": "low",
        "speed": "very slow",
        "energy": "normal"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-6727_10344_000056_000000",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/6727/10344/6727_10344_000056_000000.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-6727",
        "content": "Others, therefore, held that this luminous nebula continues in existence, but so closely attached to the sun as to be indistinguishable.",
        "style_prompt": "M_p-high_s-normal_e-normal",
        "gender": "M",
        "pitch": "high",
        "speed": "normal",
        "energy": "normal"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-6727_10344_000056_000002",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/6727/10344/6727_10344_000056_000002.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-6727",
        "content": "On this account it is held by some that the sun's body was made out of this nebula.",
        "style_prompt": "M_p-normal_s-slow_e-normal",
        "gender": "M",
        "pitch": "normal",
        "speed": "slow",
        "energy": "normal"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-6727_10344_000056_000003",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/6727/10344/6727_10344_000056_000003.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-6727",
        "content": "This, too, is impossible to those at least who believe that the sun is different in its nature from the four elements, and naturally incorruptible.",
        "style_prompt": "M_p-low_s-normal_e-low",
        "gender": "M",
        "pitch": "low",
        "speed": "normal",
        "energy": "low"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-6727_10344_000056_000004",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/6727/10344/6727_10344_000056_000004.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-6727",
        "content": "For in that case its matter cannot take on another form.",
        "style_prompt": "M_p-low_s-slow_e-normal",
        "gender": "M",
        "pitch": "low",
        "speed": "slow",
        "energy": "normal"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-6727_10344_000057_000002",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/6727/10344/6727_10344_000057_000002.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-6727",
        "content": "Thus, then, in the production of this light a triple distinction was made between light and darkness. First, as to the cause, forasmuch as in the substance of the sun we have the cause of light, and in the opaque nature of the earth the cause of darkness.",
        "style_prompt": "M_p-low_s-slow_e-low",
        "gender": "M",
        "pitch": "low",
        "speed": "slow",
        "energy": "low"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-6727_10344_000058_000003",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/6727/10344/6727_10344_000058_000003.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-6727",
        "content": "Nor does the nature of a luminous body seem to admit of the withdrawal of light, so long as the body is actually present; though this might be effected by a miracle.",
        "style_prompt": "M_p-low_s-normal_e-normal",
        "gender": "M",
        "pitch": "low",
        "speed": "normal",
        "energy": "normal"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-6727_10344_000058_000006",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/6727/10344/6727_10344_000058_000006.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-6727",
        "content": "We hold, then, that the movement of the heavens is twofold.",
        "style_prompt": "M_p-normal_s-slow_e-low",
        "gender": "M",
        "pitch": "normal",
        "speed": "slow",
        "energy": "low"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-6727_10344_000058_000007",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/6727/10344/6727_10344_000058_000007.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-6727",
        "content": "Of these movements, one is common to the entire heaven, and is the cause of day and night.",
        "style_prompt": "M_p-normal_s-normal_e-normal",
        "gender": "M",
        "pitch": "normal",
        "speed": "normal",
        "energy": "normal"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-6727_10344_000058_000008",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/6727/10344/6727_10344_000058_000008.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-6727",
        "content": "This, as it seems, had its beginning on the first day.",
        "style_prompt": "M_p-normal_s-slow_e-normal",
        "gender": "M",
        "pitch": "normal",
        "speed": "very slow",
        "energy": "normal"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-6727_10344_000058_000009",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/6727/10344/6727_10344_000058_000009.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-6727",
        "content": "The other varies in proportion as it affects various bodies, and by its variations is the cause of the succession of days, months, and years.",
        "style_prompt": "M_p-normal_s-slow_e-normal",
        "gender": "M",
        "pitch": "normal",
        "speed": "very slow",
        "energy": "normal"
    }
]